{"tid":1423397,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[正向思想] 藍黃握手","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:51:20.000Z","uid":174541,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d4390770657e8bcb59c960fa4f8e8ad1492d284f","tid":1423397,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"無論你係藍絲中立定黃底都好，你要記住<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地都係香港人</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府係為人民服務! 人民係唔應該畏懼政權!我地愛嘅係中國，唔係中國共產黨。我地係中國人，唔係中共人！<br />\n<br />\n示威係一個意識，激進係一個趨勢。背後無大台，無人可以掌控，但卻可以解散。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">關鍵在於政府!</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者係一個個體!拉也拉不完</span></span><br />\n你指責示威者暴力 破壞社會，卻未曾想過如何解決。寄望着「報應」「拘捕」等不設實際的想法簡直笑大人個口。示威者無十萬都有幾萬，就算判監了都冇位。難道你想劃個九龍半島出來給示威者?哪怕到時平均居住面積也無牢房麽大。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深究其根 還原基本步</span></span><br />\n示威是一個意識，一個被捕兩個站起來。再演化下去只會變焦土。到時樓市大跌 經濟下滑非人所願。唯有落實雙普選，人人都可以為自己發聲，人人都可以選自己的代表。這才是百利而無一害。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">偏偏就是這個無能林鄭</span></span><br />\n為了一己私利 苟延殘存，令到我們不能努力拼博，重拾東方之珠的光彩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寄望示威自動解散....<br />\n不如逼使政府行雙普選！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認同請分享</span></span>"},{"pid":"4adc4dca22adda2c321cf0a3239eb74a4dd194c5","tid":1423397,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d56fa7ce13b9ad4481ed164a2f6ff8a8aa1b2899","tid":1423397,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:50:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df82e858411b0189c43ad71096489949c51ea5ec","tid":1423397,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"6d1e38079e8404b533d6cd8eb82c59de724a32a8","tid":1423397,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"81da277841966db192cf31ce79a4a8663e4ba621","tid":1423397,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"民意就係咁黎"},{"pid":"ceda78352965e12be23f9274af6f1239038b6979","tid":1423397,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"用依個論述去就服"}]}